ger of the year for  prior to founding metwest tad was codirector of fixed income at hotchkis and wiley he was also a portfolio manager and vice president at pimco tad holds a bachelor’s degree in physics from yale university a master’s degree in applied mathematics from university of southern california and an mba from ucla anderson videos no videos yet tags wealth building investment banking financial advisor economy and finance business growth investing asset pricing request information add to list   related speakers view all leon black chairman and ceo apollo global management llc christopher m schroeder internetmedia ceo venture investor writer on star nouriel roubini world renowned economist tony cardenas us congressman christopher ailman chief investment officer california state teachers  cate ambrose president and executive director latin american pri margaret anderson executive director fastercures tony blair former prime minister great britain and northern ir joseph coughlin director agelab massachusetts institute of technology madelyn antoncic vice president and treasurer the world bank peter diamandis chairman and ceo x prize foundation author jean case ceo case foundation strive masiyiwa founder and executive chairman econet group mohamed elerian former ceo and cochief investment officer pacific  niall ferguson britishamerican historian laurence a tisch profes david foster producer and songwriter chairman verve music group freda lewishall executive vice president and chief medical officer  cecilia arradaza director communications and policy fastercures pierre beaudoin president and ceo bombardier inc francesco guerrera financial editor the wall street journal more like tad   speakerpedia about terms privacy dmca rivelle tcw total return strategy intact welcome company site log in subscribe register membership home portfolio stocks bonds funds etfs cefs markets tools real life finance discuss investing ideas fund analyst picks picks by category fund pick